<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Sobre BURGCALC</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      min-height: 100vh;
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      background: #f7f4ee;
      color: #211a16;
    }

    header {
      background: #211a16;
      color: #fff8ef;
      padding: 18px clamp(16px, 4vw, 48px);
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 18px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 1.6rem;
    }

    nav {
      display: flex;
      gap: 14px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    nav a {
      color: #f2c078;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    main {
      width: min(960px, calc(100% - 32px));
      margin: 32px auto;
    }

    .painel {
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid #e4ddd2;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 24px;
      box-shadow: 0 14px 35px rgba(33, 26, 22, 0.08);
    }

    .foto-integrantes {
      margin-top: 22px;
      margin-bottom: 22px;
    }

    .foto-integrantes img {
      display: block;
      width: 100%;
      max-height: 520px;
      object-fit: cover;
      object-position: center;
      border-radius: 8px;
      border: 1px solid #e4ddd2;
    }

    .foto-integrantes figcaption {
      margin-top: 10px;
      color: #695f58;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .integrantes {
      display: grid;
      gap: 8px;
      margin: 0;
      padding-left: 20px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>BURGCALC</h1>
    <nav aria-label="Navegacao BURGCALC">
      <a href="<%= basePath %>/calculo">Calculo</a>
      <a href="<%= basePath %>/sobre">Sobre</a>
      <a href="<%= basePath %>/help">Help</a>
      <a href="<%= basePath %>/login?ready=1">Login</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="painel">
      <h2>Sobre o projeto</h2>
      <p>BURGCALC calcula o custo de producao de hamburgueres a partir dos custos dos ingredientes, embalagem, quantidade produzida e margem de lucro desejada.</p>

      <h2>Integrantes</h2>
      <figure class="foto-integrantes">
        <img src="<%= basePath %>/images/integrantes-burgcalc.png" alt="Foto dos integrantes do projeto BURGCALC">
        <figcaption>Foto dos integrantes do BURGCALC</figcaption>
      </figure>
      <ul class="integrantes">
        <li><strong>Andre Domingues Teixeira</strong></li>
        <li><strong>Pedro Henrique Kachan</strong></li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
